{"tid":1284841,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我係廢中，唔衝得可以做咩 - 致同樣都是中坑但想行多步既朋友","createTime":"2019-07-04T10:33:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T09:14:30.000Z","uid":4161,"like":225,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"f137d063a71402e872cee10f3dbcece3aa1e8fc7","tid":1284841,"uid":4161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T10:33:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">首先，年青人，對唔住</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我垃圾，我無用，我念在家中兩老，念在一份帶來穩定收入既工作，唔想家中嬌妻擔憂，唔想屋企個化骨龍無得開飯，我無行前，我頂多去下遊行，612經過現場企行人路</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">你地好叻，仁義禮智勇兼備，叻到我覺得自己阻住地球轉，更加令我安心咁行埋一邊，見證你地創造一個又一個歷史，不斷為香港添加動人既歷史時刻</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">去到呢刻，我會諗有咩我地呢班廢中較你地容易做到，而且對件事有幫助呢?</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">相信好多中年人，不論男女，都係諗緊呢件事，唔好諗，我俾埋方法你，大家一齊做</span><br />\n<br />\n首先分析返我地有咩班後生相對少D<br />\n1) 錢，照計咁鍚身做到廢中都係因為有唔少利益框住；<br />\n2) 傳意能力 (分析能力/表達能力)，同樣，心理想偏向運動既都應該讀過下書，分析能力唔會差，再加上社會經驗較多，我地知道咩時候講咩人地會易入耳;<br />\n呢兩樣好多人或者後生仔都有，但接下來就係緊要既野:<br />\n3) 人脈，做到廢中，你係自己個行或者任何圈子點都有少少地位，分分鐘係老細或者頭目級，講句野俾NOBODY係有說服力，或者根本賣你怕;<br />\n暫時係咁多，諗到再加<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">咁可以做咩幫到手?</span>拋磚引玉俾少少建議，絕對安全，絕對合法，唔阻你好耐，俾埋LINK你<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">1) 培育有骨氣傳媒</span><br />\n香港得一間有骨氣既傳媒係唔夠，大家要不斷幫助有骨氣，會報導真相既傳媒，避免一個死人台獨大，培養自己小朋友同家人多角度吸收資訊同分析能力，做得廢中個千幾蚊你跌都跌左<br />\n支持蘋果日報連結：<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/campaign/hkad_subscription.html?utm_campaign=hkad_20190617_trial_subscription&amp;utm_medium=internal&amp;utm_source=hkad&amp;utm_content=inhouse_ad&amp;_branch_match_id=675267706346569861\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcampaign%2Fhkad_subscription.html%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_20190617_trial_subscription%26utm_medium%3Dinternal%26utm_source%3Dhkad%26utm_content%3Dinhouse_ad%26_branch_match_id%3D675267706346569861&d=3FM1mHFWgl829bPTLnnFI1Ln0p5rLcPQxw7X33U7JQw%3D&h=c19937cd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcampaign%2Fhkad_subscription.html%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_20190617_trial_subscription%26utm_medium%3Dinternal%26utm_source%3Dhkad%26utm_content%3Dinhouse_ad%26_branch_match_id%3D675267706346569861&h=2ccd589f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/campaign/hkad_subscription.html?utm_campaign=hkad_20190617_trial_subscription&amp;utm_medium=internal&amp;utm_source=hkad&amp;utm_content=inhouse_ad&amp;_branch_match_id=675267706346569861</a><br />\n支持立場妹妹連結：<a href=\"https://mystand.thestandnews.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmystand.thestandnews.com%2F&d=3FM1mHFWgl829bPTLnnFI1Ln0p5rLcPQxw7X33U7JQw%3D&h=c649e885\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmystand.thestandnews.com%2F&h=f3bb6897\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mystand.thestandnews.com/</a><br />\nNOW CABLE個堆自己訂<br />\n文宣登廣告就量力而為，支持幾多都好點都支持下<br />\n應該仲有好多，以下歡迎補充<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">有事就買定物資</span><br />\n午餐肉又好，水又好，廢中有的是錢，買多少少幫百佳抬價不為過，你屋企人用唔曬食唔曬就拎去接濟有需要朋友。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">運用自己影響力</span><br />\n做得廢中，可能有班人跟你搵食，唔知有無人睇廚房佬條片，無一個伙計還口，點解? 唔係因為廚房佬感化到佢地，而係佢地唔敢出聲。係自己有影響力既群體入面，FB又好，WHATSAPP群又好，得閑講下自己分析論據，幫佢地個腦洗白。有班人會覺得你係老闆會英明D，你咁講實有你道理之類，慢慢導佢地。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">吸納中間派，莫屌票</span><br />\n相信好多同年紀既人成日口講我討厭政治，我唔理黃藍我反對暴力之類之類。你話佢地港豬，永遠無法叫醒裝睡的人等等係無意思的。呢班人一係掛住搵錢個腦咩都唔諗，一係就只係識做返工既野，個腦係空心既。唔緊要，你擺野入去，唔好話佢地，讚佢地有能力先，慢慢發揮自己既傳意能力，引導佢睇多少少，慢慢等佢地自覺為香港出左分力，叫佢地動用資金撐下立場之類，呢類人一定會認自己係好人，安份守己，你就用呢條路出發，慢慢引導佢，最緊要係不斷口頭讚賞佢，等佢慢慢試下試下走下前D走下前D，當教小朋友一樣就得。記住，不要指責，不要指責。對一個唔識分析太多，你用反面既語氣佢只會覺得你係攻擊佢，咁完全無意思。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">重建家庭關係，決不分化，一個都不能少</span><br />\n好多家中長輩係深藍，都係出自一個愛子女之心，唔想仔女受傷。對廢中既父母黎講，佢地會緊張你份工，緊張你無仔生，緊張你俾唔到家用佢。我地作為廢中唔似後生咁可能仲要家人養，仲要分分鐘係家庭經濟支柱聲都可以大D。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但講到尾，大家都係愛大家，除左本身會傷害自己家人既變態以外，家人最後既歸屬都係家人。</span>係呢一點而言做論述，講下例如通過左條例我可能連工都無埋俾人取代呀，唔知踩中咩位俾人送上去個孫就無得食呀之類。記住，你唔會改變到佢地所有諗法，你只要將佢地拉返去中立就得。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">講返俾佢聽成家分開兩個陣營互相指責既話，只有林鄭先會得益，大家掛住互片既話佢就有位抖氣</span>，呢個係好毒既離間之計，千萬千萬不要中計。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">血債票償，一票不能少</span><br />\n用返我地既影響同傳意能力，記得自己投票，叫身邊人投票，投邊面唔使講啦。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">聘請年青義士</span><br />\n呢場仗有排打，我地既年青人即將承受慘痛既代價，佢地可能有人會被控，無人肯請，我地廢中當中有招聘請人能力既，請佢地，咁有行動力既後生仔一定幫到手過班老SEAFOOD。<br />\n<br />\n拋磚引玉完，我無野講了，如果都有中佬中女有建設性意見，大家集思廣益下<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不要分化，對準目標，五點訴求，缺一不可</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"6941bb8caccff8d6c9b9476c31ed748057e4a306","tid":1284841,"uid":93350,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T10:36:22.000Z","msg":"推 不分化 不割蓆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f7df017655f4fe23e13061b93ceaba7f6b3ca9a","tid":1284841,"uid":44181,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T10:38:47.000Z","msg":"每人行多一步就好有用，推！"},{"pid":"fdbb87e90ac591a277a13915d5f461a6b4120ee0","tid":1284841,"uid":261043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T10:38:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fd6730e857ab9c478d3919e2e722477df197499","tid":1284841,"uid":44174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T10:41:16.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n我無嘢講"},{"pid":"4387340b72faf4af601ab8ee9e05f611dff11e97","tid":1284841,"uid":34213,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T10:46:02.000Z","msg":"會一直課落去<br />\n有錢都買唔到"},{"pid":"8b3708367da7e8e0819eb80f4b02b70aab34eee3","tid":1284841,"uid":7716,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T10:48:21.000Z","msg":"多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有你地我地後生仔先可以無顧慮去做"},{"pid":"bc5a289e188bc5353f007cfa727716405a7be0c4","tid":1284841,"uid":109853,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T10:48:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ae450cc320c3a5fa6138e36e0e7930937aba07c1","tid":1284841,"uid":240004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T10:57:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我無野講"},{"pid":"c32cb82247237adfc9430a1c9aecbace1cc36972","tid":1284841,"uid":254594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T10:58:50.000Z","msg":"錢真係唔知點幫<br />\n以前有大台就捐大台<br />\n而家都唔知點捐<br />\nD後生仔自己出錢又出力 睇見心酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21a7a341866886b54fc10849f4df2b5092c01c16","tid":1284841,"uid":140309,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T11:05:42.000Z","msg":"其實好簡單，有野餐活動帶個人出黎就得，人數對我地黎講好重要"},{"pid":"1b8539b9adf5ee90487422adbe9d32a24cd7008e","tid":1284841,"uid":4161,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"c32cb82247237adfc9430a1c9aecbace1cc36972","tid":1284841,"uid":254594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T10:58:50.000Z","msg":"錢真係唔知點幫<br />\n以前有大台就捐大台<br />\n而家都唔知點捐<br />\nD後生仔自己出錢又出力 睇見心酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T11:08:24.000Z","msg":"支持傳媒<br />\n蘋果<br />\n立場<br />\n獨立媒體網之類<br />\n月捐又得<br />\n單次捐又得<br />\n<br />\n買物資，之後派街坊<br />\n你再有錢d既攪個關愛基金都得"},{"pid":"150136e125bc107375f6016ba4113ab24b0a054a","tid":1284841,"uid":4161,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"21a7a341866886b54fc10849f4df2b5092c01c16","tid":1284841,"uid":140309,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T11:05:42.000Z","msg":"其實好簡單，有野餐活動帶個人出黎就得，人數對我地黎講好重要"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T11:10:02.000Z","msg":"呢個基本盤黎，但好多廢中如我真心怕呢樣怕個樣，所以先有感而發講返唔行前係後面都唔表示咩都唔可以做"},{"pid":"4451a8e0dc244241e7cc84a85e9b50b21c8503bf","tid":1284841,"uid":206386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T11:11:46.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7011a8c68d71fe9cac88f08cb6b0f7704e358749","tid":1284841,"uid":259820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T11:12:10.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b32167ffd11eacc202d8f5e53948047c4feaddf7","tid":1284841,"uid":180114,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T11:12:30.000Z","msg":"全民健身計劃<br />\n<br />\n黎緊我地進行義教，識，唔識都可以歡迎咁多位巴絲加入<br />\n<br />\n提提大家 呢個谷唔講任何政治 <br />\n只係單純想出嚟約大家做下健身 <br />\n記住 我地健身目的係為左以後俾人追可以跑快啲，搬野可以搬重啲,有危險可以保護到自己！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/NZ0BlxTpuh58PNn1sCyW0A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FNZ0BlxTpuh58PNn1sCyW0A&d=3FM1mHFWgl829bPTLnnFI1Ln0p5rLcPQxw7X33U7JQw%3D&h=5f96ef36\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/NZ0BlxTpuh58PNn1sCyW0A</a>"},{"pid":"2a053e31be6be78ab9d18248ea7957334ab0789a","tid":1284841,"uid":205339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T11:12:39.000Z","msg":"吹歸英風加強國際壓力，引起國際關注<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1284874\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1284874</a>"},{"pid":"705e66b339dc2aae2ed08e66ac66a61c32ba69fe","tid":1284841,"uid":159271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T11:16:16.000Z","msg":"[url]200萬人既社運購物平台<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1267584\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1267584</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區[/url]<br />\n<br />\n有興趣可加入，<br />\n你既社會經驗，可能會幫到我地"},{"pid":"d411a31c0eafcb4ce753f478cd4f8700e5f019bf","tid":1284841,"uid":155066,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T11:18:02.000Z","msg":"得架喇, 做到自己可以做既野啦, 唔使咁多嗲, 心照!"},{"pid":"fea29daf33af71b38fe9d4d55e62c2ada4d0fe44","tid":1284841,"uid":4161,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T11:27:01.000Z","msg":"岩岩見到<br />\n中佬中女們出手啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n留意到好多人想課多啲金畀蘋果。  嗱， 我教你<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1284832\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1284832</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4265f582a75bd615801287883769dfbb9c9ddf1d","tid":1284841,"uid":40250,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c32cb82247237adfc9430a1c9aecbace1cc36972","tid":1284841,"uid":254594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T10:58:50.000Z","msg":"錢真係唔知點幫<br />\n以前有大台就捐大台<br />\n而家都唔知點捐<br />\nD後生仔自己出錢又出力 睇見心酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T11:35:24.000Z","msg":"星火同盟，不二之選"},{"pid":"ab6e3ccb68fe2d4da1bc8bbf775930219e54926f","tid":1284841,"uid":110509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c32cb82247237adfc9430a1c9aecbace1cc36972","tid":1284841,"uid":254594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T10:58:50.000Z","msg":"錢真係唔知點幫<br />\n以前有大台就捐大台<br />\n而家都唔知點捐<br />\nD後生仔自己出錢又出力 睇見心酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T11:41:50.000Z","msg":"立場<br />\n星火<br />\n傳真社<br />\n蘋果"},{"pid":"09e31c3685f919cbdc3ad2b30367712545399253","tid":1284841,"uid":90421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T11:42:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ac8fb8f69bae29a0308dc3dd0287bd6f923dba1","tid":1284841,"uid":49456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T11:44:15.000Z","msg":"野食其實唔洗<br />\n你捐一皮野出黎print傳單<br />\n啲傳單多到壓死人都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ff847e538ad2ccf6b9889b64180d92eda229ef2","tid":1284841,"uid":264192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T11:49:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2dad2df399661e138a9dcf2c93fea511d91cdec9","tid":1284841,"uid":143708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T11:50:10.000Z","msg":"再唔係有時間 <br />\njoin下年青人派傳單同街站嘅活動都得<br />\n行過見到買少少凍飲比佢地支持下又得<br />\n將啲文宣圖sd去唔同群組亦得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n千奇唔好覺得自己幫唔到手"},{"pid":"3bfda3b7ffe053f11f442d8ae11594ac03bb6da1","tid":1284841,"uid":268516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T12:01:28.000Z","msg":"可以做針<br />\n多啲留意吓對家做緊乜<br />\n見到有唔妥就通報<br />\n<br />\n中坑應該易啲令對家無咁有戒心"},{"pid":"44aa805a804c1078836e184fdd4c186fe649b6c6","tid":1284841,"uid":161098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T12:24:43.000Z","msg":"「有班人會覺得你係老闆會英明D」<br />\n<br />\n真係有咁嘅人？香港腦細多過老闆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58d6f44c6ab1e1f9da22e9f1ca1755503557241b","tid":1284841,"uid":4705,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T12:33:07.000Z","msg":"和理非中感染廢中先有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n後生嘅同佢哋傾只會被屌廢青聽唔入耳<br />\n要靠你哋理性分析比班廢老廢中聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5769523cff2e1be8bf4225c5fc9643da050af7f5","tid":1284841,"uid":190962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T12:53:57.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">我無嘢講</code></pre>"},{"pid":"94fee61b302ddb2ea515665f4bde23da6a298ae8","tid":1284841,"uid":71656,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T12:54:24.000Z","msg":"傳單同口罩好重要<br />\n好多人仲用緊普通口罩.."},{"pid":"a7a0e7e9edf4239e9db227394db3992ce23bbc8b","tid":1284841,"uid":4161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44aa805a804c1078836e184fdd4c186fe649b6c6","tid":1284841,"uid":161098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T12:24:43.000Z","msg":"「有班人會覺得你係老闆會英明D」<br />\n<br />\n真係有咁嘅人？香港腦細多過老闆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T13:52:25.000Z","msg":"真係有，好多人年齡階級先決，講咩睇左你身份地位先"},{"pid":"2d7cf9153a9318594fed4c34ce965a4c14723767","tid":1284841,"uid":232687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T13:53:45.000Z","msg":"多謝"},{"pid":"4f2ba93914990199c1e777a6312763f0a9f90d89","tid":1284841,"uid":4161,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T13:53:53.000Z","msg":"同埋我地呢班中坑既影響力係比自己想像大<br />\n無人咁講我地唔做野攪攪震廢青<br />\n單係呢點而言要吸納遊離份子同淺藍係較易"},{"pid":"310580db28d4a338009dddcdfe8384bd762b8ce1","tid":1284841,"uid":86686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T13:56:01.000Z","msg":"巴打，我仲廢你好多<br />\n多謝你"},{"pid":"07b308b2dc5f775ad8eb43e64a92e9ffc936d108","tid":1284841,"uid":72859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T13:56:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/GzfbXtQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGzfbXtQ.png&h=4e59ec53&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6ae92204a165d667bac79954c00cc8b91f42570b","tid":1284841,"uid":71459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f137d063a71402e872cee10f3dbcece3aa1e8fc7","tid":1284841,"uid":4161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T10:33:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">首先，年青人，對唔住</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我垃圾，我無用，我念在家中兩老，念在一份帶來穩定收入既工作，唔想家中嬌妻擔憂，唔想屋企個化骨龍無得開飯，我無行前，我頂多去下遊行，612經過現場企行人路</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">你地好叻，仁義禮智勇兼備，叻到我覺得自己阻住地球轉，更加令我安心咁行埋一邊，見證你地創造一個又一個歷史，不斷為香港添加動人既歷史時刻</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">去到呢刻，我會諗有咩我地呢班廢中較你地容易做到，而且對件事有幫助呢?</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">相信好多中年人，不論男女，都係諗緊呢件事，唔好諗，我俾埋方法你，大家一齊做</span><br />\n<br />\n首先分析返我地有咩班後生相對少D<br />\n1) 錢，照計咁鍚身做到廢中都係因為有唔少利益框住；<br />\n2) 傳意能力 (分析能力/表達能力)，同樣，心理想偏向運動既都應該讀過下書，分析能力唔會差，再加上社會經驗較多，我地知道咩時候講咩人地會易入耳;<br />\n呢兩樣好多人或者後生仔都有，但接下來就係緊要既野:<br />\n3) 人脈，做到廢中，你係自己個行或者任何圈子點都有少少地位，分分鐘係老細或者頭目級，講句野俾NOBODY係有說服力，或者根本賣你怕;<br />\n暫時係咁多，諗到再加<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">咁可以做咩幫到手?</span>拋磚引玉俾少少建議，絕對安全，絕對合法，唔阻你好耐，俾埋LINK你<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">1) 培育有骨氣傳媒</span><br />\n香港得一間有骨氣既傳媒係唔夠，大家要不斷幫助有骨氣，會報導真相既傳媒，避免一個死人台獨大，培養自己小朋友同家人多角度吸收資訊同分析能力，做得廢中個千幾蚊你跌都跌左<br />\n支持蘋果日報連結：<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/campaign/hkad_subscription.html?utm_campaign=hkad_20190617_trial_subscription&amp;utm_medium=internal&amp;utm_source=hkad&amp;utm_content=inhouse_ad&amp;_branch_match_id=675267706346569861\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcampaign%2Fhkad_subscription.html%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_20190617_trial_subscription%26utm_medium%3Dinternal%26utm_source%3Dhkad%26utm_content%3Dinhouse_ad%26_branch_match_id%3D675267706346569861&d=3FM1mHFWgl829bPTLnnFI1Ln0p5rLcPQxw7X33U7JQw%3D&h=c19937cd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcampaign%2Fhkad_subscription.html%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_20190617_trial_subscription%26utm_medium%3Dinternal%26utm_source%3Dhkad%26utm_content%3Dinhouse_ad%26_branch_match_id%3D675267706346569861&h=2ccd589f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/campaign/hkad_subscription.html?utm_campaign=hkad_20190617_trial_subscription&amp;utm_medium=internal&amp;utm_source=hkad&amp;utm_content=inhouse_ad&amp;_branch_match_id=675267706346569861</a><br />\n支持立場妹妹連結：<a href=\"https://mystand.thestandnews.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmystand.thestandnews.com%2F&d=3FM1mHFWgl829bPTLnnFI1Ln0p5rLcPQxw7X33U7JQw%3D&h=c649e885\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmystand.thestandnews.com%2F&h=f3bb6897\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mystand.thestandnews.com/</a><br />\nNOW CABLE個堆自己訂<br />\n文宣登廣告就量力而為，支持幾多都好點都支持下<br />\n應該仲有好多，以下歡迎補充<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">有事就買定物資</span><br />\n午餐肉又好，水又好，廢中有的是錢，買多少少幫百佳抬價不為過，你屋企人用唔曬食唔曬就拎去接濟有需要朋友。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">運用自己影響力</span><br />\n做得廢中，可能有班人跟你搵食，唔知有無人睇廚房佬條片，無一個伙計還口，點解? 唔係因為廚房佬感化到佢地，而係佢地唔敢出聲。係自己有影響力既群體入面，FB又好，WHATSAPP群又好，得閑講下自己分析論據，幫佢地個腦洗白。有班人會覺得你係老闆會英明D，你咁講實有你道理之類，慢慢導佢地。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">吸納中間派，莫屌票</span><br />\n相信好多同年紀既人成日口講我討厭政治，我唔理黃藍我反對暴力之類之類。你話佢地港豬，永遠無法叫醒裝睡的人等等係無意思的。呢班人一係掛住搵錢個腦咩都唔諗，一係就只係識做返工既野，個腦係空心既。唔緊要，你擺野入去，唔好話佢地，讚佢地有能力先，慢慢發揮自己既傳意能力，引導佢睇多少少，慢慢等佢地自覺為香港出左分力，叫佢地動用資金撐下立場之類，呢類人一定會認自己係好人，安份守己，你就用呢條路出發，慢慢引導佢，最緊要係不斷口頭讚賞佢，等佢慢慢試下試下走下前D走下前D，當教小朋友一樣就得。記住，不要指責，不要指責。對一個唔識分析太多，你用反面既語氣佢只會覺得你係攻擊佢，咁完全無意思。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">重建家庭關係，決不分化，一個都不能少</span><br />\n好多家中長輩係深藍，都係出自一個愛子女之心，唔想仔女受傷。對廢中既父母黎講，佢地會緊張你份工，緊張你無仔生，緊張你俾唔到家用佢。我地作為廢中唔似後生咁可能仲要家人養，仲要分分鐘係家庭經濟支柱聲都可以大D。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但講到尾，大家都係愛大家，除左本身會傷害自己家人既變態以外，家人最後既歸屬都係家人。</span>係呢一點而言做論述，講下例如通過左條例我可能連工都無埋俾人取代呀，唔知踩中咩位俾人送上去個孫就無得食呀之類。記住，你唔會改變到佢地所有諗法，你只要將佢地拉返去中立就得。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">講返俾佢聽成家分開兩個陣營互相指責既話，只有林鄭先會得益，大家掛住互片既話佢就有位抖氣</span>，呢個係好毒既離間之計，千萬千萬不要中計。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">血債票償，一票不能少</span><br />\n用返我地既影響同傳意能力，記得自己投票，叫身邊人投票，投邊面唔使講啦。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">聘請年青義士</span><br />\n呢場仗有排打，我地既年青人即將承受慘痛既代價，佢地可能有人會被控，無人肯請，我地廢中當中有招聘請人能力既，請佢地，咁有行動力既後生仔一定幫到手過班老SEAFOOD。<br />\n<br />\n拋磚引玉完，我無野講了，如果都有中佬中女有建設性意見，大家集思廣益下<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不要分化，對準目標，五點訴求，缺一不可</span></strong></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T13:56:36.000Z","msg":"多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多中年人都只會覺得我哋搞事"},{"pid":"3dd91af3c5afe5307e9e594001beb34b35d14ac8","tid":1284841,"uid":270307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b32167ffd11eacc202d8f5e53948047c4feaddf7","tid":1284841,"uid":180114,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T11:12:30.000Z","msg":"全民健身計劃<br />\n<br />\n黎緊我地進行義教，識，唔識都可以歡迎咁多位巴絲加入<br />\n<br />\n提提大家 呢個谷唔講任何政治 <br />\n只係單純想出嚟約大家做下健身 <br />\n記住 我地健身目的係為左以後俾人追可以跑快啲，搬野可以搬重啲,有危險可以保護到自己！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/NZ0BlxTpuh58PNn1sCyW0A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FNZ0BlxTpuh58PNn1sCyW0A&d=3FM1mHFWgl829bPTLnnFI1Ln0p5rLcPQxw7X33U7JQw%3D&h=5f96ef36\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/NZ0BlxTpuh58PNn1sCyW0A</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T13:58:20.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"2bc896a1a6fd0c3195f78042a2f9d59c5dff1b9c","tid":1284841,"uid":182774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:02:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4c30f3b37d78e22049ceb8a991686f7b4a452fbe","tid":1284841,"uid":212003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:03:42.000Z","msg":"推一推"},{"pid":"339b3831aad6f388b4a56b6e541419f2e49289ac","tid":1284841,"uid":226296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:06:15.000Z","msg":"Agger"},{"pid":"d6c2a1a47d13db7a22dde987e77d1294372c274e","tid":1284841,"uid":266424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:14:28.000Z","msg":"我都係中坑，我都想做啲野。因為你地我發現香港原來仲有救&hellip;我已支持蘋果了。亦一直睇Now唔睇cctvb好耐，因為我屋企係裝左統計用戶收看，所以我更加絕對不能睇cctvb！我會盡力出錢支持你地"},{"pid":"ad85dabf664874c09a63463592a54a64a5dcc240","tid":1284841,"uid":266620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:20:18.000Z","msg":"唔分化唔割蓆，有錢出錢，有力出力！！！！！！！！！！推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af0a1f297abb8eb89e7b27e9cff848580e5a3c34","tid":1284841,"uid":142007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:22:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11cecec2700f9d83c461f042c09c6c9c4f768c86","tid":1284841,"uid":90946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:26:18.000Z","msg":"擺街站果陣陪佢地一齊留係度<br />\n班藍絲廢中見得小貓幾隻，個個個樣又細個就㩒住佢地黎恰<br />\n一多人，有班大人係度佢地即刻收曬皮"},{"pid":"d487a86ba3eeea7474e0521d2e2e85eddaf0c959","tid":1284841,"uid":258465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:27:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ace588a086dcec9944b65f397cc377918fedf62a","tid":1284841,"uid":61697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:27:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6b11f388a38acdd3a5f320d8decef2ffc6fcdc43","tid":1284841,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:29:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1173e3013eb76dcc81a3e860dae9641be4f1ff9c","tid":1284841,"uid":268516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f2ba93914990199c1e777a6312763f0a9f90d89","tid":1284841,"uid":4161,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T13:53:53.000Z","msg":"同埋我地呢班中坑既影響力係比自己想像大<br />\n無人咁講我地唔做野攪攪震廢青<br />\n單係呢點而言要吸納遊離份子同淺藍係較易"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:31:15.000Z","msg":"呢個認同<br />\n如果中學生走埋去啲廢老度講道理<br />\n90%俾廢老覺得食鹽多過佢地食米<br />\n<br />\n中坑傾呢啲，起碼無左個barrier先"},{"pid":"1e3a56b284587649e565e20a4571902ff67a8aeb","tid":1284841,"uid":271064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f137d063a71402e872cee10f3dbcece3aa1e8fc7","tid":1284841,"uid":4161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T10:33:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">首先，年青人，對唔住</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我垃圾，我無用，我念在家中兩老，念在一份帶來穩定收入既工作，唔想家中嬌妻擔憂，唔想屋企個化骨龍無得開飯，我無行前，我頂多去下遊行，612經過現場企行人路</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">你地好叻，仁義禮智勇兼備，叻到我覺得自己阻住地球轉，更加令我安心咁行埋一邊，見證你地創造一個又一個歷史，不斷為香港添加動人既歷史時刻</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">去到呢刻，我會諗有咩我地呢班廢中較你地容易做到，而且對件事有幫助呢?</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">相信好多中年人，不論男女，都係諗緊呢件事，唔好諗，我俾埋方法你，大家一齊做</span><br />\n<br />\n首先分析返我地有咩班後生相對少D<br />\n1) 錢，照計咁鍚身做到廢中都係因為有唔少利益框住；<br />\n2) 傳意能力 (分析能力/表達能力)，同樣，心理想偏向運動既都應該讀過下書，分析能力唔會差，再加上社會經驗較多，我地知道咩時候講咩人地會易入耳;<br />\n呢兩樣好多人或者後生仔都有，但接下來就係緊要既野:<br />\n3) 人脈，做到廢中，你係自己個行或者任何圈子點都有少少地位，分分鐘係老細或者頭目級，講句野俾NOBODY係有說服力，或者根本賣你怕;<br />\n暫時係咁多，諗到再加<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">咁可以做咩幫到手?</span>拋磚引玉俾少少建議，絕對安全，絕對合法，唔阻你好耐，俾埋LINK你<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">1) 培育有骨氣傳媒</span><br />\n香港得一間有骨氣既傳媒係唔夠，大家要不斷幫助有骨氣，會報導真相既傳媒，避免一個死人台獨大，培養自己小朋友同家人多角度吸收資訊同分析能力，做得廢中個千幾蚊你跌都跌左<br />\n支持蘋果日報連結：<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/campaign/hkad_subscription.html?utm_campaign=hkad_20190617_trial_subscription&amp;utm_medium=internal&amp;utm_source=hkad&amp;utm_content=inhouse_ad&amp;_branch_match_id=675267706346569861\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcampaign%2Fhkad_subscription.html%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_20190617_trial_subscription%26utm_medium%3Dinternal%26utm_source%3Dhkad%26utm_content%3Dinhouse_ad%26_branch_match_id%3D675267706346569861&d=3FM1mHFWgl829bPTLnnFI1Ln0p5rLcPQxw7X33U7JQw%3D&h=c19937cd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcampaign%2Fhkad_subscription.html%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_20190617_trial_subscription%26utm_medium%3Dinternal%26utm_source%3Dhkad%26utm_content%3Dinhouse_ad%26_branch_match_id%3D675267706346569861&h=2ccd589f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/campaign/hkad_subscription.html?utm_campaign=hkad_20190617_trial_subscription&amp;utm_medium=internal&amp;utm_source=hkad&amp;utm_content=inhouse_ad&amp;_branch_match_id=675267706346569861</a><br />\n支持立場妹妹連結：<a href=\"https://mystand.thestandnews.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmystand.thestandnews.com%2F&d=3FM1mHFWgl829bPTLnnFI1Ln0p5rLcPQxw7X33U7JQw%3D&h=c649e885\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmystand.thestandnews.com%2F&h=f3bb6897\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mystand.thestandnews.com/</a><br />\nNOW CABLE個堆自己訂<br />\n文宣登廣告就量力而為，支持幾多都好點都支持下<br />\n應該仲有好多，以下歡迎補充<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">有事就買定物資</span><br />\n午餐肉又好，水又好，廢中有的是錢，買多少少幫百佳抬價不為過，你屋企人用唔曬食唔曬就拎去接濟有需要朋友。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">運用自己影響力</span><br />\n做得廢中，可能有班人跟你搵食，唔知有無人睇廚房佬條片，無一個伙計還口，點解? 唔係因為廚房佬感化到佢地，而係佢地唔敢出聲。係自己有影響力既群體入面，FB又好，WHATSAPP群又好，得閑講下自己分析論據，幫佢地個腦洗白。有班人會覺得你係老闆會英明D，你咁講實有你道理之類，慢慢導佢地。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">吸納中間派，莫屌票</span><br />\n相信好多同年紀既人成日口講我討厭政治，我唔理黃藍我反對暴力之類之類。你話佢地港豬，永遠無法叫醒裝睡的人等等係無意思的。呢班人一係掛住搵錢個腦咩都唔諗，一係就只係識做返工既野，個腦係空心既。唔緊要，你擺野入去，唔好話佢地，讚佢地有能力先，慢慢發揮自己既傳意能力，引導佢睇多少少，慢慢等佢地自覺為香港出左分力，叫佢地動用資金撐下立場之類，呢類人一定會認自己係好人，安份守己，你就用呢條路出發，慢慢引導佢，最緊要係不斷口頭讚賞佢，等佢慢慢試下試下走下前D走下前D，當教小朋友一樣就得。記住，不要指責，不要指責。對一個唔識分析太多，你用反面既語氣佢只會覺得你係攻擊佢，咁完全無意思。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">重建家庭關係，決不分化，一個都不能少</span><br />\n好多家中長輩係深藍，都係出自一個愛子女之心，唔想仔女受傷。對廢中既父母黎講，佢地會緊張你份工，緊張你無仔生，緊張你俾唔到家用佢。我地作為廢中唔似後生咁可能仲要家人養，仲要分分鐘係家庭經濟支柱聲都可以大D。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但講到尾，大家都係愛大家，除左本身會傷害自己家人既變態以外，家人最後既歸屬都係家人。</span>係呢一點而言做論述，講下例如通過左條例我可能連工都無埋俾人取代呀，唔知踩中咩位俾人送上去個孫就無得食呀之類。記住，你唔會改變到佢地所有諗法，你只要將佢地拉返去中立就得。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">講返俾佢聽成家分開兩個陣營互相指責既話，只有林鄭先會得益，大家掛住互片既話佢就有位抖氣</span>，呢個係好毒既離間之計，千萬千萬不要中計。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">血債票償，一票不能少</span><br />\n用返我地既影響同傳意能力，記得自己投票，叫身邊人投票，投邊面唔使講啦。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">聘請年青義士</span><br />\n呢場仗有排打，我地既年青人即將承受慘痛既代價，佢地可能有人會被控，無人肯請，我地廢中當中有招聘請人能力既，請佢地，咁有行動力既後生仔一定幫到手過班老SEAFOOD。<br />\n<br />\n拋磚引玉完，我無野講了，如果都有中佬中女有建設性意見，大家集思廣益下<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不要分化，對準目標，五點訴求，缺一不可</span></strong></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:32:46.000Z","msg":"推"}]}